  "prompt": "What are best computer games?",
  "response": "Determining the \"best\" computer games can be subjective and varies depending on individual preferences, genres, and platforms. However, some games are widely acclaimed for their gameplay, story, graphics, and overall impact. Here are some popular and highly regarded computer games across various genres:\n\n### Action/Adventure:\n1. **The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt** - Renowned for its rich storytelling, expansive open world, and deep character development.\n2. **Grand Theft Auto V** - Known for its vast open world, engaging story, and online multiplayer mode.\n3. **Red Dead Redemption 2** - Praised for its stunning visuals, detailed world, and compelling narrative.\n\n### Role-Playing Games (RPG):\n1. **Dark Souls III** - Celebrated for its challenging gameplay, intricate level design, and atmospheric world.\n2. **Cyberpunk 2077** - Notable for its ambitious open world and deep narrative, despite its controversial launch.\n3. **Divinity: Original Sin 2** - Acclaimed for its deep tactical combat and rich story.\n\n### First-Person Shooters (FPS):\n1. **DOOM Eternal** - Known for its fast-paced action and intense gameplay.\n2. **Half-Life: Alyx** - A groundbreaking VR experience with immersive gameplay and story.\n3. **Call of Duty: Warzone** - Popular for its battle royale mode and consistent updates.\n\n### Strategy:\n1. **Civilization VI** - Celebrated for its depth, strategic complexity, and replayability.\n2. **Total War: Three Kingdoms** - Known for its blend of turn-based strategy and real-time battles.\n3. **Starcraft II** - Renowned for its competitive multiplayer and balanced gameplay.\n\n### Simulation:\n1. **The Sims 4** - Popular for its life simulation gameplay and expansive customization options.\n2. **Cities: Skylines** - Acclaimed for its detailed city-building mechanics and modding community.\n3. **Microsoft Flight Simulator** - Celebrated for its realistic flight simulation and stunning graphics.\n\n### Indie Games:\n1. **Hades** - Praised for its engaging combat, deep narrative, and beautiful art style.\n2. **Celeste** - Known for its challenging platforming and touching story.\n3. **Stardew Valley** - Beloved for its relaxing farming gameplay and charming visuals.\n\n### Multiplayer:\n1. **Among Us** - Popular for its social deduction gameplay and accessibility.\n2. **Fortnite** - Known for its battle royale mode and constant updates.\n3. **Minecraft** - Celebrated for its sandbox gameplay and creative possibilities.\n\nThese are just a few examples, and the landscape of gaming is constantly evolving with new releases and updates. Personal preferences will ultimately determine which games are considered the best for any individual player.",
